title: SIEGE OF THE EMPIRE - Medieval Kingdoms Total War 1212AD Gameplay
description:
Medieval Kingdoms Total War 1212AD Gameplay - This is another online siege battle in medieval Kingdoms.  Jackie and I are attacking a great Eastern City as the Kingdom of Jerlusam and the Cuman Empire.  The two armies defending the city are the Latin Empire and the Trebizond Empire.  Enjoy the Epic Siege :D 

Jackie's Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/Jackiefishhhhhh


If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
